ygData.messageBody:
Who all still keeps their book? hehe i really think it does bring you luck
as my skill hasn't increased much lately. I'm at an average skill since i
stopped at the patch 105 i think. And wanted to tell you slig that your in
the right area. Kelethin and Surefall are the best places to sell for a few
reasons, one is they are highly traveled, and also that barbarian warriors
can use bows near surefall. as well as of course the rangers, and also in
kelethin you have all the different races comming in to crushbone all the
time hearing tells. both help. Just thought i'd say hello since it's been
forever since i posted last and good to see some other fletchers on povar :)

Ranale of Povar.
